Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.48,0:00:26.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,輸血就到這裡吧  沒存貨了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.85,0:00:31.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.14,0:00:33.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身體感覺很輕鬆了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.29,0:00:36.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.35,0:00:41.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,普通人早掛了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.51,0:00:43.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定會翹辮子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.83,0:00:45.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小招
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.01,0:00:51.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,堵上性命的戰鬥馬上就要開始了
